Texts.Chs: 造物有能量签名，是的。不同的是。编码信息。凯文的。“此地无凯三百两。”  ...令人担忧。嗯... 饼干的痕迹。
Texts.Eng: Artifact had energy signature, yus. Different. Encoded message. Kevin's. "There was no Kevin." That's...concerning. Well...cookie trail.

Texts.Chs: 在^orange;极暗大塔图书馆^reset;中找到^orange;神器^reset;
Texts.Eng: Find the ^orange;artifact^reset; in the ^orange;Dark Pagoda Library^reset;

Texts.Chs: 英雄参观图书馆！对吗？偶尔会把事件弄错顺序。凯文可能去了那里。去看看。
Texts.Eng: Hero visits the library! Right? Get events out of order sometimes. Kevin probably went there. Go look.
